OL,4,CLeicester postman returns Father's Day
OL,5,Cletter sent to heaven
OL,6, A mother whose eight-year-old daughter
OL,7, posted a Father's Day letter addressed
OL,8, to her dad in heaven said she was
OL,9, overwhelmed when it was returned to her
OL,10, by a postman.
OL,12,FThe postman, who recently lost his own
OL,13,Ffather, managed to track down Sarah
OL,14,FTully after a social media appeal.
OL,16,FHe said he feared the letter, which he
OL,17,Ffound in a Leicester post box on
OL,18,FMonday, would have been thrown away.
OL,20,FMs Tully said she planned to keep the
OL,21,Fletter in a box for her daughter.
